steps.description:
Tests every field in `regular`: `n`, `radius`, `center` (x/y), and `rotation`. Rotation is set to `"t"` so it animates with wall-clock time even without a playback slider.

All four fields independently accept slider variables or any valid expression.

```json
{
  "type": "animated_polygon",
  "regular": { "n": "N", "radius": "R", "center": ["cx","cy","0"], "rotation": "t" }
}
```
